Package: mintdb
Title: Minimal Integration Toolkit for Databases
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Seokhoon", family = "Joo", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "seokhoonj@gmail.com")
Description: 'mintdb' (Minimal Integration Toolkit for Databases) provides
    a unified interface for connecting to multiple database backends 
    (MariaDB, MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQLite, ODBC) using the 'DBI' framework. 
    It supports optional connection pooling via 'pool' and includes simple 
    environment-based helpers for connection setup and management.
